# sonotxt secrets (age-encrypted)

Age identity: ~/.age/identity.txt
Age public key: age14w3x4l8l9x9yqjg99zumxr0u527eqnwktkh0agad44gmkt7dqevstrg4zz

## Files

testnet-service-key.age  — Paseo Asset Hub deployer/service EVM key
mainnet-service-key.age  — Polkadot Asset Hub service EVM key (ecdsa via subkey)
vast-api-key.age         — vast.ai API key for GPU instance management

## Decrypt

    age -d -i ~/.age/identity.txt secrets/mainnet-service-key.age

## GitHub environments

Secrets are also stored in GitHub environments (testnet / mainnet):
  SONO_RPC_URL       — eth-RPC endpoint
  SONO_CONTRACT      — TXT proxy contract address
  SONO_SERVICE_KEY   — EVM private key for service operations

